# zenbot

Zen distribution system, happily interfacing with a specific team communication
service named Slack.

## Usage

```
docker build -t zenbot .
docker run -P zenbot
```

## The other sort of usage

You say:

>/zen explicit

Channel sees:

>Explicit is better than implicit.


